
ZeroConf
========

Publish the service of type ``_http._tcp`` (a usual web server) with only three ``TXT``
records::

    path=<PATH to browsable pages>
    opds=<PATH to the root of OPDS>
    fbreader=<PATH to info.xml for FBReader>

.. note::
   All paths must have the leading '/'

Reading Lists
=============

Reading lists allow to group books available in the library.

